            . I am a <rs id="t18220417-206-viclabel1087" type="occupation">rope and twine maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-206-victim1884 t18220417-206-viclabel1087"></join>, and live at Mile End, New Town, the prisoner lives in the parish; I was going to the ground about twenty minutes before six o'clock, and one James gave me information, I went after the prisoner, and found him with two other boys, I found the two lopers in his pocket, he said nothing about it, the wheel bands were stolen off the wheels.</p>
               <p>
            
